Focus Logic (HIGH PRIORITY)

User Story:
As a student, I want the app to detect when I am on productive websites so that I can earn XP to level up my character progression. 

Tasks:
•	Define a list of productive domains (GitHub, Google Docs, Notion)
•	Detect active browser tab
•	Implement XP formula (XP = Time × Multiplier)
•	Display focus timer UI
•	Create a level system
•	Design XP bar
•	Design health/mana bars

Distraction Penalty (MEDIUM PRIORITY)

User Story:
As a user, I want my character to sleep if I spend too much time on distracting websites.

Tasks:
•	Define blacklist sites (Instagram, X, TikTok)
•	Track time spent (>5 minutes)
•	Trigger sleep state
•	Apply 10% XP penalty
•	Show “character sleeping” UI

Feedback System (LOW PRIORITY)

User Story:
As a user, I want to receive feedback, so I know when I am losing focus.

Tasks:
•	Push notification (“Your hero is getting tired”)
•	Visual indicator of HP decrease
•	Alert when distraction is detected

